                    University of Technology<br>
                    Department of Computer Science<br>
                    <a href="mailto:contact@stagio.edu">contact@stagio.edu</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-divider"></div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center footer-bottom-text">
            <div>2025-2026 Stag.io. L3TI Workshop Project.</div>
